{"tid":2417231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(集思廣益)用安心出有咩即時影響","createTime":"2021-02-21T16:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T18:02:37.000Z","uid":78222,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0d79baef90c3bd1789c8a4185d242717822844e7","tid":2417231,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T16:46:58.000Z","msg":"大家如果諗到安心出行係<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">即時有害</span></span><br />\n就可以遊說更多人反對個濕鳩apps<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">對象：</span></span><br />\n廢老&amp;藍絲親戚<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">方向：</span></span><br />\n佢地傾向<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"teal\">短視</span></span>，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"teal\">即時利益</span></span><br />\n因為佢地<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"teal\">在乎</span></span>嘅係<span class=\"teal\"><span class=\"x-large\">錢 返工 食飯</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">忌：</span></span><br />\n不用講長遠問題，私隱直送支那，Dna收集，集中營，禁足，如果佢地識諗長遠就代表有用腦，自然唔會裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">換位思考：</span></span><br />\n會裝嘅人<span class=\"teal\"><span class=\"x-large\">著重當前利益</span></span>，有安心出行可以返工食飯唔洗寫紙(慳時間)，對佢地黎講仲方便咗。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">總結：</span></span><br />\n佢地對私隱唔在乎係因為，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"teal\">呢一刻</span></span>裝完私隱無曬都好，真係唔會<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"teal\">即刻損害</span></span>到佢利益，裝完銀行又唔會小咗錢，所以會覺得我地鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a7a808a687bdc0570e0151509b7d9af1c69742","tid":2417231,"uid":78222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T16:48:06.000Z","msg":"求即時利益損害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗黎諗去都係長遠問題<br />\n集中營 追蹤手足唔再有抗爭畫面。。"},{"pid":"aaf5cf55fb8d2bccb46c1f875b99aedc509f7389","tid":2417231,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T16:49:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3fcc476f7c0ca12f5c93d2bf05b3c40141383a","tid":2417231,"uid":25260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T16:49:24.000Z","msg":"用曬d data，晒錢"},{"pid":"732ca9ef8bcd3a421a70c26ae965f89b79bea89e","tid":2417231,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T16:50:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">［事態危急請廣傳］</span><br />\n<br />\n資料<span class=\"red\">安心</span>被盜竊<br />\n　　<span class=\"red\">出行</span>靠佢心都怯</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/61E1oXn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F61E1oXn.png&h=ccfbdd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>今日割五城，明日割十城，然後得一夕安寢。起視四境，而秦兵又至矣。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>［事態危急請廣傳］</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>最後致眾五毛糖尿愛滋中風花柳七孔流血橫街暴斃全家陪葬</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"ec48a669f5363cfffb59787fbe46252b8f0919f8","tid":2417231,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b3fcc476f7c0ca12f5c93d2bf05b3c40141383a","tid":2417231,"uid":25260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T16:49:24.000Z","msg":"用曬d data，晒錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T16:50:38.000Z","msg":"thank you bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有得諗<br />\n雖然依家多數都係無限plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗到手機食電 因為長開不斷upload<br />\n但唔裝又唔知幾食電"},{"pid":"68d10d631b597184426bffde249ff7387b5d115c","tid":2417231,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T16:51:32.000Z","msg":"求<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">即時利益損害</span></span>"},{"pid":"d483c3193fa30f0eb98887d10049517a59d8f385","tid":2417231,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T16:51:38.000Z","msg":"所有手機資料被偷哂<br />\n連你網銀apps資料都拿到"},{"pid":"329e5a8fa47f82d6a00a9761305b51da2718359c","tid":2417231,"uid":78222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d483c3193fa30f0eb98887d10049517a59d8f385","tid":2417231,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T16:51:38.000Z","msg":"所有手機資料被偷哂<br />\n連你網銀apps資料都拿到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T16:53:45.000Z","msg":"我認同架<br />\n但又未至於即時被盜扣佢錢<br />\n嚇唔到短視撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7efb0aaecc6cacc699c613945d94cb431d94b2","tid":2417231,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T16:55:30.000Z","msg":"目前黎講同溫層都一定唔會裝<br />\n下一步要係煽動藍絲屌鳩政府<br />\n所以真係好撚緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33607d02825a56f5b494679112564e034eedfa86","tid":2417231,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T16:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c9bab7841f36d7888124aa8738d648f886ef6d8","tid":2417231,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T16:56:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116b